Package: libgpod4
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libimobiledevice-1.0-6 (>= 1.3.0), libplist-2.0-4 (>= 2.3.0), libusb-1.0-0 (>= 2:1.0.21), libusbmuxd-2.0-7 (>= 2.1.0)
Description: library to read and write songs and artwork to an iPod
 libgpod is a library to read and write songs, playlists, artwork and
 other content to Apple iPod devices. It supports iPod Classic, Nano,
 Shuffle, Mini, Touch, and iPhone via the iTunesDB, iTunesCDB, and
 SQLite database formats.

